9 minutes ago, KeenGaming said:

The readme for SVE says I need Kopernicus, doesn't it? I'll try it though.

Kopernicus has never been a requirement - just an optional componant that would allow SVE to place rings on Jool. No Kopernicus = no rings, nothing more. Thus, as was mentioned two pages back (I think), Kopernicus doesn't work with this until it get's the 1.1 update treatment as well.

Try removing all mods and reinstall sve by itself to see if the issue persists. Also forget about kopernicus for the time being it's not compatible. Try that first.  Then read this. It's like the Bible.
